#### 2.2 — Predictive Search with Product Images 🔍 `HIGH IMPACT`
**Current:** Full-screen search with trending tags but no live results
**Proposed — Cinematic Search Upgrade:**
- 🔮 **Live product results** as you type (debounced 300ms)
- 🖼️ **Product thumbnails** with name + price in results
- 📂 **Category grouping** — "Products", "Collections", "Journal" sections
- ⌨️ **Keyboard navigation** — arrow keys to navigate results
- 🕰️ **Recent searches** — localStorage history with clear option
- ✨ **Result entrance animation** — staggered fade-in

