#### 2.3 — Mega Menu Visual Upgrade 📂
**Current:** Dropdown with category links and featured image
**Proposed:**
- 🖼️ **Full-width mega panel** with 3 sections: Categories | Featured | Promo
- 🎬 **Product card hover preview** — hovering a category shows related image
- 🏷️ **Sale badge** on promotional items
- ✨ **Staggered column animation** — each column slides in with delay
- 🌈 **Category color accents** — subtle left border with category color

---

### 🔴 Phase 3: Experience Enhancements (2-3 hours)
> *Make it feel alive and world-class*

#### 3.1 — Header Micro-Interactions ✨
- 🔄 **Nav hide on scroll down, show on scroll up** (smart sticky)
- 📏 **Header height shrink** on scroll (68px → 56px with smooth transition)
- 🌗 **Auto dark/light mode** — detect hero image contrast and switch nav colors
- 🎵 **Subtle sound on cart add** — tiny satisfying click (optional, with mute)

```css
nav.compact {
  height: 56px;
  transition: height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
}
nav.compact .nav-logo {
  font-size: 16px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
}
nav.hidden {
  transform: translateY(-100%);
  transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);
}
```

#### 3.2 — Seasonal Theme System 🌸
- 🎄 **Festival themes** — subtle header accents for Diwali, Christmas, etc.
- 🌸 **Seasonal colors** — spring pink, summer gold, autumn copper, winter silver
- 🏷️ **Dynamic promo bar** — change announcement based on current sale/season

#### 3.3 — Social Proof in Header 👥
- 👀 **"X people viewing"** — small live counter near logo
- 🛒 **"Someone just bought..."** — small toast notification
- ⭐ **Trust badges** — "4.9★ Rated" small badge in header

